item.title: 2025 Year Recap!
item.description: 2025 was definitely the wildest year of my life! Left my hometown of 36 years, bought a crib, sold a crib, did a 14 city comedy tour, met hundreds of amazing people on said comedy tour, hugged children, lifted heavy, ate good food, traveled, said goodbye to things that weren’t serving me, and most importantly - soaked up all the love! I hope it was a good year for you guys and that you’re all excited for what’s to come. Thank you for all your support this year!
